org.eclipse.cdt.utils.elf

Class ElfHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.cdt.utils.elf.ElfHelper

  • public class ElfHelper
extends Object
    ElfHelper is a wrapper class for the Elf class to provide higher level API for sorting/searching the ELF data.
